 Itâ€™s an exciting time for our company as we grow throughout stores in New York and beyond. And weâ€™re looking for someone like YOU to ensure our customers have a great time while utilizing our technology.
 About the Role:
 Brand Ambassador is a critical role at Caper, as they serve as the integral link between the customer and the development of the product. You will help improve the product based on feedback real users provide in the field.
 As the Brand Ambassador, you will be the face of the Caper Cart and be the first impression for our brand and the stores we represent.
 Responsibilities include but are not limited to:
 Engaging with customers as they enter the store; demonstrate how the Caper products works
 Assisting customers throughout their experience to ensure their journey is smooth and seamless from start to finish
 Acting as the go-to resource for all customer needs by ameliorating customer issues as they arise
 Training store staff on how to use the Caper products
 Gathering feedback from customers on their experience day to day and during user testing
 Communicating data/feedback with product team and engineers to improve the Cart as it evolves
 You are:
 Friendly, personable, able to build lasting relationships with customers and store staff
 Willing to go out of your way to help the customer, to provide exceptional customer service in order to drive usage and ensure the customer is as satisfied as possible so they want to use the Cart again and again
 Able to think on your feet and problem solve on the spot as issues arise
 Ambitious, sales driven, and willing to grow at a small technology start-up
 Interested in technology and how technology shapes the retail landscape
 You have:
 Any previous working experience as an on-site promoter, or in retail and/or customer service
 Customer-oriented approach
 Demonstrated experienced driving exceptional customer service
 This role provides flexible hours and scheduling
 Min commitment:  20-30 hours per week, no limit as to max!
